take place on April 14, will further strengthen the relationship 
between the two countries, Foreign Ministry spokesman Ferhat 
Ataman said today. 
  In an interview with XINHUA today, Ataman said that the 
relationship between Turkey and China is based on the mutual 
respect of territory integrity. 
  "We believe that our trade and other relations, especially 
the economic relations, can be further developed," the minister 
said. 
