<H3> <TI>   Supervision Ministry Delegation Visits Philippines </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Supervision Ministry Delegation Visits Philippines </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW0904003394 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 1438 
