BFN 

  [Text] Jinan, April 12 (XINHUA) -- Weihai, a port city in 
east China's Shandong Province and China's nearest city to the 
Republic of Korea (ROK), will have regular trade fair or 
discussions with the ROK. 
  This has been been approved by the Ministry of Foreign Trade 
and economic cooperation recently. 
  So far this is the only officially ratified annual 
discussion 
of its kind in China. 
