Sino-ROK economic and trade discussion. The first of subsequent 
discussions this year has been scheduled for in September. 
  The Ministry of Foreign Trade and Economic Cooperation and 
the local government have pinned high hopes on this year's 
discussion, as 2,000 foreign businessmen, including 1,000 from 
the ROK, will be invited to the fair. The others will be from 
Japan, Singapore, Taiwan, Hong Kong, Macao, Europe and the 
United States. 

